Dialogs.Dialog: Okay, please show me your stomach.
Hmm？ What...！？ That's for kids, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？
Geez. Didn't I told you to call me "Takane-sensei" when playing doctor？ Mmm.
Yes！ Wait, are we playing doctor！？
Now then, show me your stomach.
(Hmm, something's off... I should follow instructions！)
You shouldn't breathe when you wear a stethoscope, right？
It's fine. I'm hearing your breathing sound.
And you hold your breath when you hear the sound of the heart. Papa said so.
Hehehe！ But, it was a good, beautiful sound. Please, make it easier.
(I was nervous about playing doctor, we're not doing "pretend" but "simulating".)
(I was doing my best since I was a kid, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Yes. You can go to the hospital every day with Takane-sensei. I'm looking forward for it.
...I wonder if I should be a doctor, after all？
Everyone says that. I wonder what kind of doctor Manaka-chan will become.
I have never been asked, "What do you want to be when you grow up？"... Neither Papa nor Mama...
I don't think that's the case. I think both your Papa and Mama want you to choose your own path, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
It's good, Manaka wants to be a doctor. I want to help Papa... Manaka will become a doctor.
(What a nice thing！ My chest is pounding...！)
Stand still！ There is a risk of arrhythmia！
Wait a minute. I'm like this because I was moved by your story, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Who！？ I mean, that is, you know, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...！
Huh, what are you talking about！？
Don't worry, Nene-senpai. I'm breathing heavy...
Ah！ We are the best pair in beach volleyball！
(I don't know why, but now I'm in a beach volleyball match with ▲高嶺＊＊▲, ▲小早川＊▲, and ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！)
(I'm not sure, but I can't lose！)
Hehe. How was it？ My Rinko attack.
I can't help it, let's change our tactics！
But we have to do something about that attack...
Don't be fooled！ Pay attention to the other party！
Opponents... Carefully study ▲小早川＊▲ and ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲...
W-what？ That is some serious gaze...
Wait, you're staring like a perv, you know？
No！ Don't look at us so much！
Well then... I know, I'll sign it.
You see, this is the sign.
Keep an eye on my butt！
I understand！ I'll keep an eye on your butt, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
(I wonder if you're aware of the great things you say ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Alright, it's time to check the sign！
(As expected, you have a trained and toned body, yet soft where it matters ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(I can't take my eyes off it... for victory！)
Emm！ Using Nene-san as a stepping stone！？
Take this！ Overhead small kick attack！
I'm okay, your butt was firmly burned into my eyes ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
It's fine！ You're slow to notice...
(...Hmm？ If you look closely, you can see some handsome men around.)
If you want to call me your wife, you must bring what I say.
Can I marry you and do it later？
(And, this is the first time I see her like this. ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Do you want silk？ Or, do you want gold？
No no no... isn't something greener？ My, princess.
(No no no... What are they saying？)
Hah. I'm not interested in such things.
Diamond earrings, pink gold bracelet, mink coat, and Rapda bag...
Ah, and a sweet potato▼ with plenty of butter▼
I'll do it, whatever it takes, leave it to us！
Wait！ I will not allow you to run away！
Huh？ No... I don't think there is anything in the world that I can't get...
Waiter... Does that mean we're now married, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？
What do you mean？ I was waiting for you！
Because you didn't come quickly, in this case... Devote yourself to me！
I wish you could reflect on that... Geez. I was worried.
Ah, welcome. This is all for you.
I don't have time, so I'll take you home！ If you want me！
What！？ Oh, it was a dream...
My feelings were too intense this time, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
It seems I have some accumulated stress...
Yes, a mermaid... One that has longed for you...
You might think it's not true... I was watching you all this time, from this sea.
I remember now. The ship I was on was wrecked. Did you help me？
Thank you, I owe you one.
You are kind and beautiful, my life saver. I want to welcome you as a princess.
Thank you... Thank you so much...
But, you can talk this way！ What's wrong！？
...You're the prince of a nation, I'm the daughter of the king of mermaids. I'm not allowed to be with you.
Yes, it's a medicine that will make me human.
If I take this medicine, I can be with you.
Little mermaid, please take that medicine！
...Princess, does that medicine have side effects？
Yes... But I don't think there is anything more important to me than being with you.
I'm glad！ I've become a human！
Your voice！ So loud！ Turn down the volume！
Too bad... That was the side effect...
That's terrible！ Prince！ I love you！
My name is Manaka Takane. It's a pleasure to meet you.
Same here. It's a pleasure to make your acquittance.
Oh dear. Don't be so nervous.
You keep silent, I'll do this...
(It is okay, I can do this.)
If you have any questions, ask away understood？
(I should ask "What are your hobbies are？")
Is there anything would you like to ask？
(I should ask about her favorite foods.)
(I should ask "What do you like to eat？")
("What is your favorite dish？" please ask.)
Keep calm... Think of your daughter's marriage. Calm down, please？
Well, I like digging for potatoes...
(Her father's gaze...！ I wonder if it's okay to continue.)
Manaka-san, do you have a favorite dish？
Yes. Boiled potatoes, university potatoes... Little potatoes before this...
I won't allow this！ I won't, I won't！
No！ Manaka！ I don't want anyone to take my Manaka away！
What！！ Who are you calling father！
It's fine Makana. You stay here. I'll go.
I'm sorry！ Don't pull my ears！
(Her mother... Kendo and Judo, combined with her father's 8th dan.)
You look so graceful, and cute wearing a kimono, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
But what did they mean with that kind of couple.
(Emm... I should ask "What are your hobbies？")
(Oh, yeah... I should ask "What do you like？")
Speak to the microphone “Ga shumi wa？”
Speak to the microphone “Tokuina ryōri wa？”
▲高嶺＊＊▲！？ I wonder where's her classroom...
It's the middle of a battle, don't let your guard down！
(It doesn't look like you can talk.)
(Don't you have time to talk, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Then why are we doing this？
Because... I also want a boyfriend！
I don't know if you see, but no.
You... What are you doing that for.
It's really cool to have a girlfriend！ I really feel that！
You'll be fine even if you fall down...
Then, what is the purpose of this battle？
Emm, I'm sorry. I'll check it again！
Trees in the schoolyard. Bells in the clock tower. Hills with cherry blossoms.
Also a church where primroses bloom, a lighthouse by the sea...
If the confession there is successful... both will be happy forever！
Then I will have a girlfriend too！
Don't you think that legend is necessary for Towano High School！？
I don't know... having to do something forcibly...
It's going to be painful for Takane...
Those who don't support the revolution must be excluded from the alliance as an outsider.
No way！.. We are together！ We can be together without that legend！ You could be happy！
We don't need a legend... The two of us... can become legends！
Sorry, Miyoshi. I will stop the revolution♪
Uh... you do have a boyfriend...
Damn it... It's fine... It's fine...
Naruto, you can take a break...
If you want, escape from here.
Wow, wait！ Emm... inside the bazooka？ Impossible！ I'm not going into！
It's okay, if you push it as hard as you can...
I'll shoot you out with this...
What's wrong, something's on your stomach！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Stand up！ If you don't, you won't win for Towano High School！
(That looks painful... Hang on！ If the ace doesn't get over this, there's no tomorrow for the club！)
Don't fall back！ You have to be firm！
Guts, guts, guts！ What's wrong with you！
(Her tears are coming out. This is her limit.)
Ah！ Coach, I still can do it！
Please！ Even if it's painful or sad... I'll be fine！
What's wrong！ I thought you could do it！
...I wonder why my heart is beating...！
(Did you end with a heart mark just now？)
I'm happy to receive the coach's ball with my whole body！
▲高嶺＊＊▲...！ I'm happy to teach to members like you！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
A dream... It was a strange dream...
I wonder if you would hate my weird dreams, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
(Today I had a date with. But, it was my first time in Shibuya with, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(It's late... It's rare for her to be so late.)
(I'm operating with just the index finger.)
Hi, yahoo！ Even a greeting like that... It's Cool, isn't it？
Instead, what do you do？ Is that okay at all？
Hehe. For the time being. Why don't we go to karaoke all night？
That's right... Wait, I can't do it all night！ Moreover, for the time being...
(I did my research because it's a date in Shibuya.)
Well, how about this？ Or was it better for it to be back？
I wonder if you also have a ribbon of that color...
Ah... Emm... this in an earring. Papa... he complained too much.
He is such a demon. Manaka makes her own decor.
That signboard？ Ivana is really cute. It's really respected.
(It's the first time I hear about it.)
Wait, I really want you to stop.
It's Ｈ／Ｋ... Emm, that changes everything.
You're doing good... What's wrong with you, it's not impossible..
...I knew it, you don't like Manaka to do this.
It's not a lie！ Whatever you do, I'll love it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Then, will you be a galman only for Manaka？
...I will！ I will be！ Let me be it, please！
Teehee▼ Manaka, kyun☆ I'm about to die♪
Well then, to buy clothes, shall we got to Salo？
You'll be a galman, right？ Come on.
Actually, when did you become like that, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
(I don't know what's on her hears.)
(Huh, is there a mobile phone like that？)
(I'm being embraced by her as a... Am I a baby！？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？)
Hmm, are you in a bad mood？
(I can't speak... I'm really a baby.)
It's because Papa isn't here？ Papa, is late.
(That's right, if you have a child, the father... Who is the father！)
He wanted to see Papa... Mama is cute, I'm kidding.
(I'm glad... I'm my own father... Hah)
(That is me. It's kind of confusing to be your own father.)
Waiting for my husband, and you...
We were married, and you were born...
One people makes two, and two people makes three...
I realized it would be nice if more families were born...
I wonder if my Papa and Mama were so happy when I was born...
Before you were born, being alone was painful...
It's okay now. Because you will be there.
(We have arrived to an uninhabited island. Just me and ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(Because I'm totally used to the island life now.)
(Well then, where did you go, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
(Hmm？ By the way, there was a water area here.)
(This is bad, I said it loud.)
(Okay, this is a classic animal cry！)
There are many on this island... I hope I won't be attacked...
(I wonder if I managed to distract you.)
There are even cats on this island...
Amazing. There is also a raccoon on this island...
I hear the cry of an UMA for the first time...
(I can't seem to get out of it.)
No way, it's not like this...
You can't peep at bathing people...
(There, there, I should just keep pushing.)
Yes, it can't be. That's not true.
I wonder how she did find out...
Speak to the microphone UMA sounds
Speak to the microphone like a mysterious creature
Speak to the microphone “Imitate an animal”
